Type of Feat: General
Prerequisite: Minimum Level 6
Specifics: You are the sort of person others want to follow.  You can have up to six party members. Bards gain a +1 bonus with Inspire Courage for having this feat.

[NOTE: Leadership only affects player created characters in Storm of Zehir. This feat does nothing when given to cohorts, or to characters in other campaigns except for bards (mentioned above).]

Use: Automatic.